models.design.project

Class QueueShareStackIntPair<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • abstracts.AbstractQueueIntPair<T>
      • models.design.project.QueueShareStackIntPair<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    HasInvariant, UnboundedStorageSpecification<Pairs<T>>

    public class QueueShareStackIntPair<T>
extends AbstractQueueIntPair<T>
implements UnboundedStorageSpecification<Pairs<T>>
    This class implements a queue that works with Pairs elements
    It is an extension of AbstractQueueIntPair and an implementation of UnboundedStorageSpecification
    As project's requirement, QueueShareStackIntPair has two QueueShareStack queues
    Two these queues are aggregations of this class. There are getter and setter for 2 these queues
    The tested instances of both queue can be built by two queues of UnreliableStack or ReliableStack
    Author:
    btdiem
